# Your LIVE website URL (required for banner QR codes that work in the real world)
# No trailing slash. Example:
VITE_SITE_URL=https://mrfirstgencricketacademy.com

# Steps for a print-ready banner QR:
# 1. Set VITE_SITE_URL above to your deployed domain
# 2. Run: npm run generate:qr
# 3. Use public/enrollment-qr.png on your banner
#
# Or visit /interested on the live site and download the QR from there.
